<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Thank You for Your Interest</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: #333333; line-height: 1.6; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background-color: #003366; color: #ffffff; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content { padding: 20px; background-color: #f9f9f9; }
        .footer { padding: 15px; text-align: center; font-size: 12px; color: #999999; }
        .highlight { color: #003366; font-weight: bold; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Thank You for Reaching Out!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <span class="highlight">{!Lead.FirstName}</span>,</p>

            <p>Thank you for your interest in our offerings. We have received your enquiry from <span class="highlight">{!Lead.Company}</span> and our team will be in touch with you shortly.</p>

            <p>You indicated interest in: <span class="highlight">{!Lead.Product_Interest__c}</span></p>

            <p>One of our dedicated sales representatives will review your submission and contact you within 1 business day to discuss how we can best support your needs.</p>

            <p>In the meantime, feel free to explore more about our solutions at <a href="https://www.exlservice.com">www.exlservice.com</a>.</p>

            <p>Warm regards,<br/>
            <strong>EXL Sales Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated response. Please do not reply directly to this email.</p>
            <p>&copy; 2026 EXL Service Holdings, Inc. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>